Celeron didn&#39;t move a muscle, keeping his gaze fixed on Leo Prime.

&quot;The transport is a prison ship operated by Maximal guards.  I worked with
them once, I&#39;m just worried about their safety,&quot; said the Pred.  &quot;I am a
Predicon out of convenience, I have no ties to the larger organization.
They gave me a workspace, so I give them my service.&quot;
On Jul 5, 2011 7:08 AM, &quot;Super Cyclonus&quot; &lt;supercyclonus@...&gt; wrote:
&gt;&gt; &lt;OLD&gt;
&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt; &quot;My name is Celeron.&quot; said the green bot, who was now clearly emitting a
&gt;&gt; Predecon signature. &quot;The ship that crashed in the ocean was an enormous
&gt;&gt; Maximal prison transport. I had some previous contact with the crew
several
&gt;&gt; megacycles ago when I assisted them with repairs.&quot;
&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt; The bot was rather short. A metalic green color with red accents. He
&gt;&gt; didn&#39;t seem at all concerned that he was standing among all these
Maximals
&gt;&gt; and Autobots.
&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt; &quot;The ship sunk to such a depth that it was impossible for me to access it
&gt;&gt; with my limited equipment. If the hull is intact, there may be survivors.
&gt;&gt; There&#39;s also a chance that the surviving prisoners escaped to the
surface.&quot;
&gt;
&gt; &lt;NEW&gt;
&gt;
&gt; LEO PRIME watched the newcomer carefully, his optics glittering as he
&gt; straighted.
&gt;
&gt; &quot;He is emmitting a Predacon energy signature.&quot; LEGACY said as he stood
&gt; from his position to the side of the stage. &quot;And another ship is
&gt; arriving as well - this one with seeming Maximal energy signatures.&quot;
&gt;
&gt; There was a nod from LEO PRIME, &quot;Good, see to it that the others are let
in.&quot;
&gt;
&gt; As they talked, TORCA and NOCTORO moved to the sides of the room,
&gt; watching CELERON. While they had no weapons out, they were clearly
&gt; reay for any trouble.
&gt;
&gt;&gt; &lt;OLD&gt;
&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt; Meanwhile...
&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt; Lord Perseus circled the area in their shuttle then landed. He and a
&gt;&gt; Maximal guard walked toward the meeting.
&gt;
&gt; &lt;NEW&gt;
&gt;
&gt; As PERSEUS and his guard approached a door in the Ark opened to allow
&gt; them entrance. The meeting was actually taking place just inside, so
&gt; they would be aware of CELERON&#39;s presence as well as everyone else who
&gt; was still present. as well as what LEO PRIME was saying to CELERON.
&gt;
&gt; LEO PRIME turned back to CELERON, &quot;Tell me, why did you, a Predacon,
&gt; bring this to our attention? I would think that this would work in
&gt; your favor, perhaps use the confusion to accomplish whatever you have
&gt; in mind.&quot; His face was registering more curiousity than distrust at
&gt; this point, although his manner was a bit reserved.
